      • addObservedLatency

        public org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.U64 addObservedLatency(org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.U64 latency)
        Append a new (presumably most recent) latency to the list. Sets the current latency if this is the first latency update performed. Note the latter serves as a latency initializer.
        参数:
        latency -
        返回:
        latency to use for the link; either initial or historical average

      • getCurrentLatency

        public org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.U64 getCurrentLatency()
        Read-only. Retrieve the currently-assigned latency for this link. Does not attempt to update or compute an average.
        返回:
        the latency; null if an initial latency has not been set
